
* alert *

Syntax:  alert [<type>]

	Enter in alert mode. When your boss stops to watching you, type
        'y' to exit from this mode.

	<type>			<means>

		c               C source listing
                p               PASCAL source listing
                d               dBASE source listing
                h               HTML source listing
		a		Assembler source listing

	Default type is 'c'.

See also: .alarm, .afk
  